<L>__{interior exterior police car night}
<A>__{wade whitehouse, driving, sits beside jill, his daughter, ten years old, wearing a black and yellow tiger plastic mask.}
<C>__{wade}
<D>__{i'm sorry for the screw up. but i couldn't help it it's too late to go trick or treating now. i couldn't help it i had to stop at penny's for the costume. and you were hungry, remember.}
