<D>__{can't you see... look out there. nobody's got their porch lights on anymore. it's too late. those hoyt kids are just out to get in trouble. see, they put shaving cream all over that mailbox there. they chopped down herb crane's new bushes. little bastards. jesus h. christ.}
<A>__{wade grimaces, holds his jaw. the fairlane swerves around broken pumpkins under a caution light.}
